  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="page active" id="pagina1">
      <div class="card-main">
        <h2 class="title"><i class="fas fa-pizza-slice me-3"></i>Pizzer&iacute;a escolar</h2>
        <p class="frase-clave">No basta con ver cu&aacute;nta pizza se us&oacute;; tambi&eacute;n importa en cu&aacute;ntas rebanadas iguales se cort&oacute;.</p>
        <div class="audio-box">
          <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p1_intro"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
          <div class="audio-label"><i class="fas fa-volume-up me-2"></i>Escucha la explicaci&oacute;n</div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="pair-row">
            <div>
              <div class="mini-frac"><span>4</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div>
              <div class="round-model pizza-4-6" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sign-card">&ne;</div>
            <div>
              <div class="mini-frac"><span>3</span><span class="linea"></span><span>4</span></div>
              <div class="round-model pizza-3-4" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-note">Aunque ambas se ven grandes, primero hay que revisar el total de rebanadas y luego las que ya se usaron.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="exercise" id="card-p1e1">
          <div class="ex-head"><span class="ex-badge">Ejercicio</span><span class="ex-sub">Escucha y toca</span></div>
          <div class="audio-box">
            <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p1_ej1"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
            <div class="audio-label">Escucha el reto y responde con el apoyo visual.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="choice-grid round-choice-grid" id="p1e1-options">
            <button type="button" class="choice-card round-card" data-value="6/8"><div class="round-model pizza-6-8" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="caption">Pizza A</div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card round-card" data-value="5/8"><div class="round-model pizza-5-8" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="caption">Pizza B</div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card round-card" data-value="4/6"><div class="round-model pizza-4-6" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="caption">Pizza C</div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card round-card" data-value="3/4"><div class="round-model pizza-3-4" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="caption">Pizza D</div></button>
          </div>
          <div class="actions"><button type="button" class="btnx main" data-action="verify">Verificar</button><button type="button" class="btnx alt" data-action="clear">Borrar selecci&oacute;n</button></div>
          <div class="feedback" id="p1e1-feedback"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page" id="pagina2">
      <div class="card-main">
        <h2 class="title"><i class="fas fa-glass-water me-3"></i>Puesto de agua fresca</h2>
        <p class="frase-clave">Las marcas de referencia ayudan a pensar si una fracci&oacute;n est&aacute; cerca de un cuarto, de la mitad o de tres cuartos.</p>
        <div class="audio-box">
          <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p2_intro"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
          <div class="audio-label"><i class="fas fa-volume-up me-2"></i>Escucha la explicaci&oacute;n</div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="jar-row">
            <div class="jar-box"><div class="jarra" style="--fill:25%"><div class="ticks eighths"></div></div><div class="caption">1/4</div></div>
            <div class="jar-box"><div class="jarra" style="--fill:50%"><div class="ticks eighths"></div></div><div class="caption">1/2</div></div>
            <div class="jar-box"><div class="jarra" style="--fill:75%"><div class="ticks eighths"></div></div><div class="caption">3/4</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-note">Si una jarra queda entre 1/4 y 1/2, entonces representa una cantidad menor que la mitad pero mayor que un cuarto.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="exercise" id="card-p2e1">
          <div class="ex-head"><span class="ex-badge">Ejercicio</span><span class="ex-sub">Escucha y toca</span></div>
          <div class="audio-box">
            <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p2_ej1"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
            <div class="audio-label">Escucha el reto y responde con el apoyo visual.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="choice-grid jar-choice-grid" id="p2e1-options">
            <button type="button" class="choice-card jar-card" data-value="3/8"><div class="jarra" style="--fill:37.5%"><div class="ticks eighths"></div></div><div class="caption">Jarra A</div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card jar-card" data-value="1/4"><div class="jarra" style="--fill:25%"><div class="ticks eighths"></div></div><div class="caption">Jarra B</div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card jar-card" data-value="5/8"><div class="jarra" style="--fill:62.5%"><div class="ticks eighths"></div></div><div class="caption">Jarra C</div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card jar-card" data-value="7/8"><div class="jarra" style="--fill:87.5%"><div class="ticks eighths"></div></div><div class="caption">Jarra D</div></button>
          </div>
          <div class="actions"><button type="button" class="btnx main" data-action="verify">Verificar</button><button type="button" class="btnx alt" data-action="clear">Borrar selecci&oacute;n</button></div>
          <div class="feedback" id="p2e1-feedback"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page" id="pagina3">
      <div class="card-main">
        <h2 class="title"><i class="fas fa-road me-3"></i>Carrera escolar</h2>
        <p class="frase-clave">En la recta num&eacute;rica, las fracciones mayores quedan m&aacute;s a la derecha y las menores m&aacute;s cerca del cero.</p>
        <div class="audio-box">
          <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p3_intro"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
          <div class="audio-label"><i class="fas fa-volume-up me-2"></i>Escucha la explicaci&oacute;n</div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="recta-box">
            <div class="recta">
              <div class="recta-line"></div>
              <div class="mark" style="left:6%"><span>0</span></div>
              <div class="mark" style="left:50%"><span>1/2</span></div>
              <div class="mark" style="left:94%"><span>1</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-note">Si avanzas hacia la derecha, la cantidad representada aumenta. La mitad siempre queda entre el inicio y el entero completo.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="exercise" id="card-p3e1">
          <div class="ex-head"><span class="ex-badge">Ejercicio</span><span class="ex-sub">Escucha y toca</span></div>
          <div class="audio-box">
            <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p3_ej1"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
            <div class="audio-label">Escucha el reto y responde con el apoyo visual.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="recta-box" id="p3e1-recta">
            <div class="recta">
              <div class="recta-line"></div>
              <div class="mark" style="left:6%"><span>0</span></div>
              <div class="mark" style="left:28.67%"><span></span></div>
              <div class="mark" style="left:50%"><span>1/2</span></div>
              <div class="mark" style="left:72.67%"><span></span></div>
              <div class="mark" style="left:94%"><span>1</span></div>
              <button type="button" class="target" data-value="1/4" style="left:28.67%"></button>
              <button type="button" class="target" data-value="1/2" style="left:50%"></button>
              <button type="button" class="target" data-value="3/4" style="left:72.67%"></button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="actions"><button type="button" class="btnx main" data-action="verify">Verificar</button><button type="button" class="btnx alt" data-action="clear">Borrar selecci&oacute;n</button></div>
          <div class="feedback" id="p3e1-feedback"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page" id="pagina4">
      <div class="card-main">
        <h2 class="title"><i class="fas fa-equals me-3"></i>Modelos equivalentes</h2>
        <p class="frase-clave">Dos fracciones pueden verse distintas y aun as&iacute; representar la misma cantidad del entero.</p>
        <div class="audio-box">
          <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p4_intro"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
          <div class="audio-label"><i class="fas fa-volume-up me-2"></i>Escucha la explicaci&oacute;n</div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="pair-row">
            <div>
              <div class="mini-frac"><span>3</span><span class="linea"></span><span>4</span></div>
              <div class="strip s4"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sign-card">=</div>
            <div>
              <div class="mini-frac"><span>4</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div>
              <div class="strip s6"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-note">Aunque cambie el n&uacute;mero de partes, la zona coloreada ocupa la misma proporci&oacute;n del entero.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="exercise" id="card-p4e1">
          <div class="ex-head"><span class="ex-badge">Ejercicio</span><span class="ex-sub">Escucha y toca</span></div>
          <div class="audio-box">
            <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p4_ej1"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
            <div class="audio-label">Escucha el reto y responde con el apoyo visual.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="choice-grid" id="p4e1-options">
            <button type="button" class="choice-card" data-value="6/8"><div class="mini-frac"><span>6</span><span class="linea"></span><span>8</span></div><div class="strip s8"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div></div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card" data-value="2/4"><div class="mini-frac"><span>2</span><span class="linea"></span><span>4</span></div><div class="strip s4"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div></div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card" data-value="8/12"><div class="mini-frac"><span>8</span><span class="linea"></span><span>12</span></div><div class="strip s12"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div></div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card" data-value="3/5"><div class="mini-frac"><span>3</span><span class="linea"></span><span>5</span></div><div class="strip s5"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div></div></button>
          </div>
          <div class="actions"><button type="button" class="btnx main" data-action="verify">Verificar</button><button type="button" class="btnx alt" data-action="clear">Borrar selecci&oacute;n</button></div>
          <div class="feedback" id="p4e1-feedback"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page" id="pagina5">
      <div class="card-main">
        <h2 class="title"><i class="fas fa-sort-amount-down me-3"></i>Ordena de menor a mayor</h2>
        <p class="frase-clave">Para ordenar, conviene pensar qu&eacute; fracci&oacute;n queda m&aacute;s cerca de cero, cu&aacute;l pasa la mitad y cu&aacute;l casi llega al entero.</p>
        <div class="audio-box">
          <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p5_intro"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
          <div class="audio-label"><i class="fas fa-volume-up me-2"></i>Escucha la explicaci&oacute;n</div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="mini-seq">
            <div class="mini-frac"><span>1</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div>
            <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <div class="mini-frac"><span>1</span><span class="linea"></span><span>2</span></div>
            <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <div class="mini-frac"><span>5</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-note">Del menor al mayor, el orden siempre avanza desde las cantidades m&aacute;s peque&ntilde;as hasta las que est&aacute;n m&aacute;s cerca de 1.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="exercise" id="card-p5e1">
          <div class="ex-head"><span class="ex-badge">Ejercicio</span><span class="ex-sub">Escucha y toca</span></div>
          <div class="audio-box">
            <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p5_ej1"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
            <div class="audio-label">Escucha el reto y responde con el apoyo visual.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="question-box">
            <div class="fraction-row">
              <div class="fraction-box"><div class="mini-frac"><span>3</span><span class="linea"></span><span>8</span></div></div>
              <div class="fraction-box"><div class="mini-frac"><span>2</span><span class="linea"></span><span>3</span></div></div>
              <div class="fraction-box"><div class="mini-frac"><span>5</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="choice-grid" id="p5e1-options">
            <button type="button" class="choice-card sequence-card" data-value="ordA"><div class="mini-seq"><div class="mini-frac"><span>3</span><span class="linea"></span><span>8</span></div><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span><div class="mini-frac"><span>2</span><span class="linea"></span><span>3</span></div><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span><div class="mini-frac"><span>5</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div></div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card sequence-card" data-value="ordB"><div class="mini-seq"><div class="mini-frac"><span>2</span><span class="linea"></span><span>3</span></div><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span><div class="mini-frac"><span>3</span><span class="linea"></span><span>8</span></div><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span><div class="mini-frac"><span>5</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div></div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card sequence-card" data-value="ordC"><div class="mini-seq"><div class="mini-frac"><span>5</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span><div class="mini-frac"><span>2</span><span class="linea"></span><span>3</span></div><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span><div class="mini-frac"><span>3</span><span class="linea"></span><span>8</span></div></div></button>
            <button type="button" class="choice-card sequence-card" data-value="ordD"><div class="mini-seq"><div class="mini-frac"><span>3</span><span class="linea"></span><span>8</span></div><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span><div class="mini-frac"><span>5</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span><div class="mini-frac"><span>2</span><span class="linea"></span><span>3</span></div></div></button>
          </div>
          <div class="actions"><button type="button" class="btnx main" data-action="verify">Verificar</button><button type="button" class="btnx alt" data-action="clear">Borrar selecci&oacute;n</button></div>
          <div class="feedback" id="p5e1-feedback"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page" id="pagina6">
      <div class="card-main">
        <h2 class="title"><i class="fas fa-bullseye me-3"></i>Cerca del entero</h2>
        <p class="frase-clave">A veces conviene pensar qu&eacute; fracci&oacute;n est&aacute; m&aacute;s cerca de 1 y cu&aacute;l todav&iacute;a se queda lejos.</p>
        <div class="audio-box">
          <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p6_intro"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
          <div class="audio-label"><i class="fas fa-volume-up me-2"></i>Escucha la explicaci&oacute;n</div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="pair-row">
            <div><div class="mini-frac"><span>1</span><span class="linea"></span><span>4</span></div><div class="strip s4"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div></div></div>
            <div><div class="mini-frac"><span>1</span><span class="linea"></span><span>2</span></div><div class="strip s4"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div><div class="seg"></div></div></div>
            <div><div class="mini-frac"><span>7</span><span class="linea"></span><span>8</span></div><div class="strip s8"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-note">La fracci&oacute;n m&aacute;s cercana a 1 es la que deja menos espacio sin completar.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="exercise" id="card-p6e1">
          <div class="ex-head"><span class="ex-badge">Ejercicio</span><span class="ex-sub">Escucha y toca</span></div>
          <div class="audio-box">
            <button type="button" class="audio-btn" data-audio="audio_p6_ej1"><i class="fas fa-play"></i></button>
            <div class="audio-label">Escucha el reto y responde con el apoyo visual.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="choice-grid" id="p6e1-options">
            <button type="button" class="choice-card" data-value="5/6"><div class="mini-frac"><span>5</span><span class="linea"></span><span>6</span></div><div class="strip s6"><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg fill"></div><div class="seg"></div></div></button>
